============================================
XBMC Mixcloud Plugin - jackyNIX/Bochi
============================================

Current version: 1.0.0 dharma
============================================

Features:
  - Browse
    - New
    - Hot
    - Popular
    - Categories
  - Search
    - Cloudcasts
    - Users
  - Url resolving (removing invalid streams)
  - Thumbnails (configurable download size)
  - History
    - Played cloudcasts
    - Search
============================================

Todo:
  - Foolproof error handling
  - Python 2.0 migration (eden)
